snippet: Serena Williams and Angelique Kerber, battling it out for the world number one ranking, are the first two women to qualify for the season-ending WTA Tour Finals in Singapore, the WTA said on Monday....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams and Angelique Kerber, battling it out for the world number one ranking, are the first two women to qualify for the season-ending WTA Tour Finals in Singapore, the WTA said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Serena Williams and Kerber Qualify for Tour Finals
headline.main: Serena Williams and Kerber Qualify for Tour Finals
